{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b8ff59f738","title":"关于中央警卫团不应设立文工团的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"773eef9356","index":0,"year":1953,"month":11,"day":5,"articleId":"b8ff59f738"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"b07023c42c","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"b8ff59f738","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在人民革命军事委员会总政治部副主任肖华1953年11月2日关于处理电报中的错误问题给毛泽东的检讨报告上。检讨报告中说：最近，我在处理电报中犯了错误，7月9日批发公安部为中央警卫团抽调文工团队员的电报，当时只注意到保证中央领导同志的安全问题，而未考虑到电报可能发生的政治影响，后经彭德怀副主席指出，才发觉错误。"},{"id":"75a1efb5f6","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"b8ff59f738","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。朱，指朱德。彭，指彭德怀，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席。罗瑞卿，当时任中央人民政府公安部部长。周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"ee5acfecdc","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"b8ff59f738","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"202f3ce695","type":"title","text":"关于中央警卫团不应设立文工团的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"b8ff59f738"},{"id":"b07023c42c","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、朱、彭、罗瑞卿、周阅，尚昆处理","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"b8ff59f738"},{"id":"75a1efb5f6","type":"paragraph","text":"根本不应设此文工团，三反后文发生此事是不应当的。肖华只负批发电报的错误，根本的错误在公安机关","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"b8ff59f738"},{"id":"ee5acfecdc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"b8ff59f738"},{"id":"71db4aea74","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年十一月五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"b8ff59f738"}],"page":{"id":"c84aaa8dad","publicationId":"maoquanji33